And yes, it's somewhat of a rant/rave.  I've brought the issue over there once before, and recieved an attitude of &quot;if you don't like it, don't read it&quot;.  That's crap, in my opinion.  Fact is, this board can determine the fate of people in game.  It determines if they sink, or swim, usually.  It should be controlled, mature, and thoughtful.  It should NOT jump to conclusions.<br>
<br>
After his post and the logs, I can see why people reacted how they did.  And yes, it was in line with their early reactions.  And YES, it was posted by a respected member.  But everyone can get hotheaded.  Everyone can get mad, and want to take the anger out on the source of it.  I'm not saying he lied, or that he did anything wrong.  But on a forum dictated by getting mad at someone, and posting your anger, there's a lot of room for exaggeration.<br>
<br>
I don't think a person who is on this form is usually innocent.  Rarely.  What I think is that people need to take a sit down, wait around, and judge based off of EVIDENCE, not the word of a person.  I don't care if that person is Tarot herself, I would not believe it until I saw proof.  Maybe it's just me. <p><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=125458"><img src="http://home.attbi.com/~briangeerlings/beredorsignature.jpg"></a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#E5E5E6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub110.ezboard.com/uwaalker.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Waalker</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>n00b!</span><br> <font color=#000033>(5/13/02 5:36:48 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub110.ezboard.com/feqasylumshitlistpeopletowatchoutforonourserver.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=729.topic&index=127>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Well...</span><hr size=1> . <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#D5D4D5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub110.ezboard.com/uzeffansilvershield.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Zeffan Silvershield</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>l33t dood!</span><br> <font color=#000033>(5/13/02 6:35:24 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub110.ezboard.com/feqasylumshitlistpeopletowatchoutforonourserver.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=729.topic&index=128>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Well...</span><hr size=1> So, lemme guess, Waalker...trying to increase post count on your ezboard account?<br>
